add YAML (.env)
| Purpose             | Tool                   |
| ------------------- | ---------------------- |
| Environment & paths | `env_config.py`        |
| User settings       | `config.yaml`          |
| Secrets             | `.env` + `os.getenv()` |
| CLI flags           | `argparse` or `typer`  |

then env_config.py and stt/config.py might need altering.



